title: I'm All Set
description:
The Chris Klemmer era of KMS has come to an end and Kirk wishes him nothing but the best in his future endeavors (00:00:10). Barstool is hosting a mini-golf tournament in the Hamptons July 13th. Justin has the most boring story from his ride home yesterday (00:30:20). Elliot Page has deemed comedians making jokes about trans people hate speech (01:07:30). J-Rock is influencing the youth and much more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kminshow
